learfix\" style=\"width:960px;position:relative\">\n<div class=\"block_thumb_slide_show\" style=\"background: #e2e2e2;text-align:left\">\n<img style data-reference-id=\"26471393\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" data-original=\"https://i-kinhdoanh.vnecdn.net/2019/05/10/1new-1557474126_680x0.jpg\" class=\"vne_lazy_image\" alt=\"10 th&#xE0;nh ph&#x1ED1; c&#xF3; nhi&#x1EC1;u t&#x1EF7; ph&#xFA; nh&#x1EA5;t th&#x1EBF; gi&#x1EDB;i\" data-component-caption=\"&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;\n	&amp;lt;strong&amp;gt;1. New York (M&#x1EF9;)&amp;lt;/strong&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;\n	S&#x1ED1; t&#x1EF7; ph&#xFA; USD: 105&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;\n	So v&#x1EDB;i n&#x103;m 2018: t&#x103;ng 2 ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;\n	New York l&#xE0; n&#x1A1;i c&#xF3; nhi&#x1EC1;u t&#x1EF7; ph&#xFA; h&#x1A1;n t&#x1ED5;ng t&#x1EF7; ph&#xFA; c&#x1EE7;a h&#x1EA7;u h&#x1EBF;t c&#xE1;c qu&#x1ED1;c gia tr&#xEA;n th&#x1EBF; gi&#x1EDB;i, b&#xEA;n c&#x1EA1;nh Trung Qu&#x1ED1;c v&#xE0; &#x110;&#x1EE9;c.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;\">\n<a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"icon_thumb_videophoto icon_thumb_zoom btn_icon_show_slide_show\"><i class=\"ic ic-expand\"></i></a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"desc_cation\"><p>\n<strong>1. New York (M&#x1EF9;)</strong><br>\nS&#x1ED1; t&#x1EF7; ph&#xFA; USD: 105<br>\nSo v&#x1EDB;i n&#x103;m 2018: t&#x103;ng 2 ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i<br><br>\nNew York l&#xE0; n&#x1A1;i c&#xF3; nhi&#x1EC1;u t&#x1EF7; ph&#xFA; h&#x1A1;n t&#x1ED5;ng t&#x1EF7; ph&#xFA; c&#x1EE7;a h&#x1EA7;u h&#x1EBF;t c&#xE1;c qu&#x1ED1;c gia tr&#xEA;n th&#x1EBF; gi&#x1EDB;i, b&#xEA;n c&#x1EA1;nh Trung Qu&#x1ED1;c v&#xE0; &#x110;&#x1EE9;c.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fck_detail width_common\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">\n<strong>Phi&#xEA;n An</strong> (<em>theo Business Insider</em>)</p>	</div>\n', 'https://i-kinhdoanh.vnecdn.net/2019/05/10/1new-1557474126_180x108.jpg', 'pending', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 'https://vnexpress.net/kinh-doanh/10-thanh-pho-